This is a placeholder for the favicon.ico file. You should replace this with a real favicon.ico file.

Since favicon.ico is a binary file, you can't create it with a text editor. You'll need to:

1. Create an icon image (16x16 or 32x32 pixels)
2. Convert it to .ico format
3. Place it in this location

For now, you can download a simple favicon or create one using free online tools. 